ciscoWanAtmConnCapability.description: The agent capabilities for CISCO-WAN-ATM-CONN-MIB in MGX8800 Series. - The capability cwAtmConnCapabilityAxsmV2R0160 is for AXSM in MGX Release 2.1.60. - The capability cwAtmConnCapabilityAxsmeV2R0160 is for AXSM-E in MGX Release 2.1.60. - The capability cwAtmConnCapabilityRpmprV2R0160 is for RPM-PR in MGX Release 2.1.60. - The capability cwAtmConnCapabilityBpxsesV3R00 is for AXSM in MGX Release 3.0.00. - The capability cwAtmConnCapabilityAxsmV3R00 is for AXSM in MGX Release 3.0.00. - The capability cwAtmConnCapabilityAxsmeV3R00 is for AXSM-E in MGX Release 3.0.00. - The capability cwAtmConnCapabilityPxm1eV3R00 is for AXSM-E in MGX Release 3.0.00. - The capability cwAtmConnCapabilityRpmprV3R00 is for RPM-PR in MGX Release 3.0.00. - The capability cwAtmConnCapabilityRpmxfV12R02 is for RPM-XF in MGX Release 3.0.00. - The capability cwAtmConnCapabilityV5R00 is for MPSM155 & VXSM in MGX Release 5.0.00.
